                   net.nemein.incidentdb Changelog
                   -------------------------------
Legend:
- All items marked with "!" represent a major API-Change that is
  not guranteed to be backwards compatible to previous versions
  which might even break existing functionality.
- All items marked with "+" represent completly new features.

2005-03-15 torben
  - Added indexer support to the component, using custom security to filter
    the search results. TODO: Move to GUIDs in the future, as Permalinks don't
    work with incidents.

2005-03-12 torben
  - Switched to the new Component Interface base class. No indexing support
    yet.

2005-02-11 torben
  - Adapted to the new Metadata system.

2004-11-10 torben
  - Filesystem transition
  - Moved to $midcom->relocate()

2004-08-02 SmallOne
  - Added swedish translation

2004-04-23
  - Switched date entry from text field to unixdate datatype that provides
    the nice calendar pop-up
  - Fixed bug with deletion of created event when Cancel is pressed
  - Added Finnish translation (Incident = Tapaus)

2004-04-04
  - Initial Checkin
